{"tid":2216773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講真一句，所有冤獄手足必需有所補償","createTime":"2020-09-25T03:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T01:49:28.000Z","uid":182935,"like":9,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"82464dcbee4e7c7f458d29bccbdbe55061b0198f","tid":2216773,"uid":182935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T03:18:10.000Z","msg":"未來一定要對呢班冤獄手足作出補償<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人建議，對所有坐過冤獄/傷殘嘅手足做出以下措施<br />\n1.所有罪名徹銷，並且再給予最少三次免罪權限，可豁免之後三次十年或以下刑期之刑責<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.終生交通費免費及終生公屋免租（如果未有公屋者可優先處理，輪候時間不多於一個月，及可自由選擇分配到邊區、邊條邨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n3.終生每月發放義士津貼，建議計算:最低工資時薪 x 1.5 x 24 x 31（唔理嗰個月有幾多日，總之一律當31日計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），如果傷殘者就另外再計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 如有任何公司拒絕聘請＆無理解僱以上手足，公司老闆及股東+所有主任級或以上員工+所有HR部門員工必定極刑處決<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他歡迎大家提出意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然一日未贏，一切都只係FF<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e01bbc2fec9498c9763c4ad3f0cdd647c89b50","tid":2216773,"uid":45558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T03:18:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9022017d1882c705b2305fe0f41b434d